snippet: Hundreds of Cypriots have staged a protest outside the presidential palace against proposed legislation aimed at helping the bailed-out country's beleaguered banks collect on bad loans....

headline.print_headline: Cypriots Protest Proposed Bank Loan Legislation
headline.main: Cypriots Protest Proposed Bank Loan Legislation

lead_paragraph: Hundreds of Cypriots have staged a protest outside the presidential palace against proposed legislation aimed at helping the bailed-out country's beleaguered banks collect on bad loans.
